Blink!

Personal Project

Blink! is part of my ongoing series of projects that aim to make everyday life more fun through goofy yet usefulobjects that connect with their inner child of every adult.

An ultrasonic sensor (which I find is a safer alternative to IR sensors) is used to detect long eye blinks, which triggers the camera placed on the glasses to capture a photo.
